text: Interstate 195 (I-195) is an Interstate highway in the U.S. state of Maryland. The highway runs from I-95 in Arbutus east to MD 170 near the Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport (BWI Airport) in Linthicum. I-195, which is also known as Metropolitan Boulevard, is the main connection between the airport and highways leading to Baltimore, Washington, and Annapolis, including I-95, MD 295, and I-97.
